latestIgtvVideos.title: SURPRISE VIDEO CALL from @shibanidandekar
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
QUARANTINE BIRTHDAY SURPISE

I wasn’t sure about my 25th birthday celebrations due to the lockdown and had very little expectation but I was surprised by the the ultimate birthday gift beyond my dreams. 
I got wished by two of the most lovely boss babes whom I totally adore from so many years. 
@shibanidandekar who is my ultimate favourite. Her style and her confident personality just steals my heart. To my surprise, I received a video call followed by a recorded video from this absolutely beautiful human being who not only wished me but made my day super special by giving me a lifetime memory. This two minute conversation with her made me fall in love with her even more. Cannot wait to meet her after this Lockdown. 
The other beautiful woman that I have been following from more than 2 years now @sazan sent me a video wish. I have mentioned it many-a-times that she is not only my favourite blogger but an inspiration to me. I admire how natural her blogging is; from her love story with @stevie_hendrix and their hardships to their relocation to Texas, I feel I have lived all with her through her Blog. I have watched Teeny grow up from the day she was born and still sleep watching her cute videos. To be able to love someone just through her blog is what inspires me to be like her. 
Social media can be about show-off or whatever ways people take it but for me it’s always been a source of connecting to people or blogs that inspire me and bring the best out of me.

To be able to get my birthday wishes from two of these incredible women is an amazing feeling and I am going to treasure this for a very long time.

Shoutout to my fam @dimple.arora.1800 @jitesh.wadhawan @nipun_10 @stuti.m7 @shailajjain for making my birthday so special. BLESSED❤️ @shibanidandekarworld @shibanidandekar_fc @4moreshotspls @4moreshottspls

May your journey together be filled with countless moments of happiness, unwavering support, and endless love. Always remember that the little things—shared smiles, quiet conversations, and holding hands through life’s ups and downs—are the most precious treasures of marriage.

Thank you for allowing us to capture your special day. It’s an honor to preserve these memories for you to cherish for years to come.

Wishing you a lifetime of love and blessings,
